speech.p:
No. There is no time, so I shall be brief.

Ask the Opposition how, if they were to reduce the community charge, they would set about doing it, and one hears that it is not their responsibility; they do not know;

they do not have a clue. That is the story of the Opposition for the past 11 years, and that is why they will stay in opposition for the next 11 years.
